snippet.title: Amber Heard and Jason Momoa interviewed by Grandma for Cosmopolitan UK
snippet.description:
For the first instalment of 'Grandmas Interview' of Cosmopolitan UK, Amber and Jason had a small chat with the lovely Barbara, about some scenes in the film and Arthur's outfits!
